(4079,0,0,49098,36095, 'A Tribute to Immortality', 'Dear $N,$B$BTales of your recent performance in the Trial of the Grand Crusader will be told, and retold, for ages to come. As the Argent Crusade issued its call for the greatest champions of Azeroth to test their mettle in the crucible of the Coliseum, I hoped against hope that beacons of light such as you and your companions might emerge from the fray.$B$BWe will need you direly in the coming battle against the Lich King. But on this day, rejoice and celebrate your glorious accomplishment and accept this gift of one of our very finest warhorses. When the Scourge see its banner looming on the horizon, hero, their end shall be nigh!$B$BYours with Honor,$BTirion Fordring'), -- A Tribute to Immortality Horde
